name: $uicideboy$
description: $uicideboy$ are an American hip-hop duo from New Orleans, Louisiana, founded in 2014 by cousins Ruby da Cherry and $crim. Via the music sharing platform SoundCloud, the duo rose to popularity for their abrasive, self-produced beats, as well as their harsh lyrical content and themes prominently featuring substance use disorder and suicidal ideation. The duo are considered one of the most popular artists in the underground rap scene. They own and operate their own label, G*59 Records, under which all of their music is released.
category: Cloud Rap, Dark Trap, Horrorcore, Underground Hip Hop, Punk Rap

name: JGRXXN
description: Jemel Green, better known as JGRXXN, J-Green, or Hollywood J is a producer and rapper from Atlanta, Georgia. He started releasing music in the late 90's and is known for being the first to incorporate Memphis-style 90's dark and cinematic beats with Atlanta-style trap beats. Him,SpaceGhostPurrp, Dj Smokey, and Mr. Sisco are the originators of phonk, a genre of rap/trap that started in the mid 2000's - early 2010's. He began his career as a member of the Blac Teflon record label from 2007 - 2012, and was also associated with Three 6 Mafia and the Hypnotize Minds label. He produced for Three 6 Mafia and toured with them for while, but was fired mulitple times, before having a complete fallout with them.

name: Shakewell
description: Shakewell is an American rapper from the San Fernando Valley in California, USA. Before starting his rap career, Shakewell was the bassist for hardcore/metalcore band Betrayal. Shakewell started making rap music in 2014 and has released a number of albums, EPs, and singles. His music ranges from drugged out, spacey trap to more melodic trap, as well as some dark trap and more aggressive songs. Shakewell was a member of Buffet Boys from 2015 - 2022, never leaving until Buffet Boys ended. Shakewell is currently signed to G59 records and is the founding member of SHAMELESS MONEY GANG ,which consists of Shakewell, Germ, and Ramirez. Shakewell is also a member of the collective All But 6 and has been since 2015. He is also the of cousin of fellow rapper Boobie Lootaveli.
